Cookies are small bits of data stored from your internet browser that can be used by websites to deliver you a better experience.

Out&Back Outdoor uses different types of cookies to help customers who want us to remember them, to stay logged into our site and to help deliver a more personalized, relevant experience. Some cookies are placed by third party services that appear on our pages to help us deliver advertisements to you across external networks. These cookies never include personal information.

You can, at any time change or withdraw your consent from the Cookie Declaration on our website.

Learn more about who we are, how you can contact us and how we process personal data in our Privacy Policy.

    Jackets Men's Outerwear PRIMALOFT® Shells Tops Water Resistant Wind Resistant

    A Patagonia classic, the Shelled Synchilla is a versatile bomber-style jacket made from durable, water-resistant nylon with a soft fleece lining. It'll be your spring and fall buddy for outdoor fun.


    • Versatile wind-resistant nylon shell is treated with a Durable Water Resistant finish
    • Lined with warm Synchilla fleece
    • Tall stand-up collar is insulated with PrimaLoft One 60g for warmth
    • Raglan sleeves free up arm movement
    • Rib-knit cuffs and hem stretch and snug in warmth
    • Patagonia Shelled Synchilla jacket has zippered hand pockets and an inner chest welted pocket, all lined with brushed tricot
